      class ConnectionManager extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • ackCheckTimer
          Map<String,CTimer> ackCheckTimer
          ackCheckTimer is a map containing the tokens of the clients and the respective timers to keep track of the ack received in response to a ping
        • ackMap
          Map<String,Boolean> ackMap
          ackMap contains the tokens of the clients and the boolean indicating whether an ack has been received from them
        • ackTime
          int ackTime
        • inactiveUsers
          List<String> inactiveUsers
          inactiveUsers is a list containing the tokens of all the inactive users
        • master
          ServerManager master
        • namesTokens
          Map<String,String> namesTokens
          namesTokens contains the usernames of the players and the respective tokens
        • synTime
          int synTime
        • synTimer
          Map<String,CTimer> synTimer
          synTimer is a map containing the tokens of the clients and the respective timers to send them a ping
        • tokenNames
          Map<String,String> tokenNames
          tokenNames contains the tokens of the players and the respective usernames
        • viewListenerMap
          Map<String,IClientListener> viewListenerMap
          viewListenerMap contains the tokens of the players and the respective listeners (i.e. ClientListenerTUI, ClientListenerGUI, ServerSocketClientHandler)
